org.jdesktop.swing.animation.demos

Class DiscreteInterpolationTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jdesktop.core.animation.timing.TimingTargetAdapter
      • org.jdesktop.swing.animation.demos.DiscreteInterpolationTest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimingTarget

    public class DiscreteInterpolationTest
extends TimingTargetAdapter
    A Swing application that demonstrates use of a DiscreteInterpolator using KeyFrames within a PropertySetter animation.

    This demo is discussed in Chapter 15 on page 410 of Filthy Rich Clients (Haase and Guy, Addison-Wesley, 2008).

    Author:
    Chet Haase, Tim Halloran
